quran[11{c,v,t}:
21,102,( yahan taq ke ) is ki aawaz bhi to nahi sunen ge. aur jo kuch un ka jee chahay ga is mein ( yani ) har terhan ke aish aur lutaf mein hamesha rahen ge
21,103,un ko ( is din ka ) bara bhaari khauf ghamgeen nahi kere ga. aur farishtay un ko lainay ayen ge ( aur kahin ge ke ) yahi woh din hai jis ka tum se wadakiya jata hai
21,104,jis din hum aasman ko is terhan lapait len ge jaisay khitton ka tomaar lapait letay hain. jis terhan hum ne ( kaayenaat ko ) pehlay pedakiya isi terhan dobarah peda kar dein ge. ( yeh ) wada ( jis ka poora karna lazim ) hai. hum ( aisa ) zaroor karne walay hain
21,105,aur hum ne nasiyaat ( ki kitaab yani torat ) ke baad Zaboor mein likh diya tha ke mere nekokaar bande malik ke waris hon ge
21,106,ibadat karne walay logon ke liye is mein ( khuda ke hukmon ki ) tableegh hai
21,107,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko tamam Jahan ke liye rehmat ( bana kar ) bheja hai
21,108,keh do ke mujh par ( khuda ki taraf se ) yeh wahi aati hai ke tum sab ka mabood khuday-e wahid hai. to tum ko chahiye ke farmanbardar ban jao
21,109,agar yeh log munh phairen to keh do ke mein ne tum ko sab ko yaksaa ( ehkaam Ellahi se ) aagah kardiya hai. aur mujh ko maloom nahi ke jis cheez ka tum se wadakiya jata hai woh ( an ) qareeb ( anay wali ) hai ya ( is ka waqt ) daur hai
21,110,aur jo baat pukaar ki jaye woh usay bhi jaanta hai aur jo tum posheeda karte ho is se bhi waaqif hai
21,111,aur mein nahi jaanta shayad woh tumahray liye azmaish ho aur aik muddat taq ( tum is se ) faida ( uthatay raho )
21,112,paighambar ne kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar haq ke sath faisla kardey. aur hamara perwar-digaar bara meharban hai isi se un baton mein jo tum bayan karte ho madad mangi jati hai
